         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Chief Secretary's Office ¶ Melbourne 24th March 1870 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ By direction of the Chief Secretary I have the honor to forward you the enclosed letter addressed to Mr Ferguson ¶ On 24 March,Odgers wr...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.03.24</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From William Odgers</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 608, unit 19, p. 170, VPRS 1187/P outward correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Chief Secretary's Office</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne 24th March 1870</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>By direction of the Chief Secretary I have the honor to forward you the enclosed letter addressed to Mr Ferguson<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>On 24 March,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Odgers wrote to William<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Ferguson: 'Mr MacPherson desires me to observe that he considers your communication altogether objectionable in its tone and not such as should have been addressed by you to the Head of the Government. Moreover any representations you may desire to make to the Chief Secretary in regard to your official position should be transmitted through Dr Von Mueller who is the Head of your Department and from whom as your Superior it will be your duty to receive instructions. I am to add that it would be well for you to hold yourself in readiness to actively engage in the work of Inspection of Forests as soon as suitable weather sets in.' (No. 609, unit 19, p. 171, VPRS 1187,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Public Record Office, Victoria).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and to request that you will be good<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>enough to hand the same to him.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I am</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. H. Odgers</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr Von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanic Gardens</p>
         </div>
